## KEYWORDS('algebra', 'factoring')
DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGchoicemacros.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$b = random(2,4,2);
$d = random(3,7,2);
$coef = $b*$b;
$t = 2*$b*$d;
$n = $d*$d;

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Factor the polynomial \($coef x^2-$t x+$n\). Your answer can be written as
\((Ax+B)^r\) with \( A\), \(B\), and \(r \)- integers
$BR where \(A\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $b;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(B\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  -$d;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(r\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  2;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.
